<tal:block  i18n:domain="novaideo" >
	<div class="contextual-help-item present-help hide-bloc">
	  <p i18n:translate="">Any member can communicate to any other member of the platform an amended version that was submitted. S/he can also transmit it to any external person, by providing the e-mail address of this external person.</p>
	  <p i18n:translate="">External persons have access to the platform, but can connect to it only if they become members.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="contextual-help-item  comment-help hide-bloc">
	    <p i18n:translate="">Any amended version that was submitted can be discussed among the participants in the working group.</p>
	    <p i18n:translate="">To start a discussion thread, you only need to specify your intention and the message that you wish to transmit to others.</p>
		<p i18n:translate="">Any participant in the working group can answer you. Reciprocally, you can answer to any message in a discussion thread.</p>
		<p i18n:translate="">You can also add to your message any element that is present in the platfom. By clicking on « Associations », you will find all the discussion threads with elements associated to this one.</p>
	</div>
</tal:block>







